    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エミル</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Emil</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エミル？
海水パンツなんて持って
どこに行ってたの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Emil? Where are you headed
off to in your swimming pants?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うん、ちょっと海に行ってたんだ。
クロエさんと一緒にね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh, I'm going to the ocean.
I'm going there with Chloe-san.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>えぇぇぇぇぇぇ！！！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whaaaaaat?!!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>女の子と二人で海で遊んでたの！？
そ、それってデートじゃない！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You went to the BEACH together with a GIRL?!
I-Isn't that just a DATE?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>え？　いや……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? No...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>私のエミルを
色気ムンムンで誘惑するなんて
絶対に許せない！！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>There is NO way I can forgive her for trying to
seduce my Emil with such a sultry charm!!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>戦争よ！！
もう戦争なんだから！！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This is war!!
She's brought about war!!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
